# Financial Risk Management Capital Requirement Amount

## identifier
de5552

## type
float

## definition
Report the value of the minimum capital requirement determined in accordance with the management capital prudential standard and held outside the statutory funds to ensure that under a range of adverse operating circumstances the company would be expected to be in a position to meet its trading commitments and adequately service its policy owners.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=FinancialRisk.ManagementCapital.Requirement.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.05
- period=instant
